text: Kadyrsha () is a rural locality (a village) in Sabyrovsky Selsoviet, Zilairsky District, Bashkortostan, Russia. The population was 105 as of 2010. There are 2 streets. == Geography == It is located 50 km from Zilair, 15 km from Sabyrovo. == References == Category:Rural localities in Zilairsky District
title: Kadyrsha
